1. create a venv (i.e., new project with separate venv)

to create a new virtual env:
python -m venv venv - to create a new virtual env

second venv is folder name:
py -3 -m venv webserver


2. create the python script.

3. run using

set FLASK_APP= servername.py
flask run

to run in dev mode so that changes will reflect as we make

set FLASK_ENV=development
flask run


4. to add a fevicon :
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='covid.ico') }}">